{"tid":445795,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逾萬中國運動員涉禁藥受查","createTime":"2017-10-23T16:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T00:02:20.000Z","uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0af092c6d9cf24a6c96cded458392b48b3b42664","tid":445795,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:49:03.000Z","msg":"逾萬位80、90年代的中國運動員被指犯禁藥，世界反禁藥組織將會介入調查。<br />\n<br />\n英國BBC報道，中國奧運代表團前隊醫薛蔭嫻（Xue Yinxian）最近於德國電視節目聲稱，80、90年代有逾1萬位中國選手服用禁藥，以提升運動表現，其中有數個項目，更有系統式犯禁藥的情況。她還表示，自己因拒絕向一位體操運動員提供違禁藥物，而被國家隊開除。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，世界反禁藥組織（WADA）表示留意到薛蔭嫻的說法，並會介入調查事件；不過，組織於亦聲明中提到，要於現在裁定30年前發生的事情十分困難。WADA於2003年引入相關禁藥條例，而追溯期限只有10年。<br />\n<br />\n另外，由於有藥檢結果呈陽性反應，中國於本月與其他8個國家，被禁止參加舉重項目的國際比賽1年。"},{"pid":"979e4e5a064995b4b609aebd0bc27914328ca9ab","tid":445795,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:52:15.000Z","msg":"咁少？"},{"pid":"a7ca51f5b0105b20b754c56784af69c5a30a44b8","tid":445795,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:54:57.000Z","msg":"等萬幾人？<br />\n肯定100%食藥打針啦"},{"pid":"151eb9b643848c353358886373388830e636de8a","tid":445795,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T00:01:05.000Z","msg":"嘔番晒啲金牌出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9bb7ad066f53d1573e35786280ac27ae5bab447","tid":445795,"uid":147945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T00:01:59.000Z","msg":"紫色尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f8d2ec9250ce74fac5b97651eb33d866fe37066","tid":445795,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T00:02:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}